  "notes": [
    "NCS 5500 does NOT support ISSU — requires traffic-impacting reload",
    "Cisco 8000 supports ISSU — but FPD auto-upgrade must be disabled during ISSU",
    "XRdocs (xrdocs.io) is the gold mine for SP operational best practices — maintained by Cisco IOS-XR engineering/TME teams",
    "No formal CVDs for Cisco 8000/NCS 5500 — the Converged SDN Transport (CST) design series on XRdocs is the equivalent",
    "IS-IS recommended over OSPFv3 for SRv6 networks"
  ],
